        <p class="section-sub">Our two-path unlock system ensures customers can always access their device after paying — whether they have internet or not.</p>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">1</div>
            <div>
              <div class="step-title">Customer pays via M-Pesa</div>
              <div class="step-desc">Payment is made using any M-Pesa channel — STK push, Paybill, or USSD. No app required to initiate payment.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">2</div>
            <div>
              <div class="step-title">Backend verifies payment</div>
              <div class="step-desc">Safaricom's Daraja webhook hits our Cloud Function within milliseconds. Payment amount, reference, and registered number are all validated.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">3</div>
            <div>
              <div class="step-title">Signed unlock command sent</div>
              <div class="step-desc">An RS256-signed unlock command is pushed to the device via FCM. If the device is offline, an HMAC SMS code is sent to the registered number.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">4</div>
            <div>
              <div class="step-title">Device verifies and unlocks</div>
              <div class="step-desc">The app verifies the signature or validates the SMS code locally against the device IMEI. If valid, the device unlocks immediately — no server round-trip needed.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
